      <th>4</th>
      <td>Node type</td>
      <td>Based on the type of node you select, clients must use either the IP\naddress (or corresponding FQDN) of any Admin Node or the IP address\n(or corresponding FQDN) of any Gateway Node to access this endpoint.</td>
